Mbali wanhu viwahulike kuwa Yesu kasegela, wamsondelela, kawalamila, na kalonga nawo mbuli za Ufalume wa Mulungu, na kawahonya wanhu wakalile wowakalile wolonda kuwahonyeza.
Viifikile chigulogulo, na waja wanahina longo na waidi wamuhitila Yesu na kumulongela, "Lagula lung'husesa lwa wanhu wahite muna yamabululu na muna yamabululu muladi wakagule ndiya na kulonda ndiya, kwaviya hano hochili ni chuwala muhala."
Yesu kawedika, "Mweye weng'heni ndiya waje." Wamwidika, "Chitali na chinhu ila magate matano na somba waidi, mbali chihite chikagule ndiya ya kuwegulila wanhu wano wose ndiya."
Kukala na wanhu malongo matano. Yesu kawalongela wanahina wake, "Muwalongele wanhu wano wakale hasi mwiivibumbila-bumbila va wanhu malongo matano-matano."
