Vino munhu kobweda choni kuipata isi yose, mbali kowagiza hebu kuhasanya ugima wake?
Fana munhu yahambonela chinyala niye na mbuli zangu, niye, Mwana wa Munhu nizamuwonela chinyala munhu iyo muna utunhizo wake na utunhizo wa Tati yangu, hamwe na wasenga wa kuulanga welile.
