Baho tukawafika wandugu, waiting'hana na cheye chila hanhu nikala nawo siku saba. Ivo uchilawa mbaka Roma.
Ndugu we Chilisito vawahulike mbuli zetu, wahita kuchisogo cha Apiyo na Hanhu hatangigwe Mizahawa Nhatu. Viwawonile wawo, Paulo kamwing'ha Mulungu mate, moyo wake wangala.
